---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

// SEO: Schema para Tickets
const ticketsSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Offer",
  "name": "FIFA World Cup 2026 Tickets",
  "description": "Official information about ticket costs, sales phases, and hospitality packages for the 2026 World Cup.",
  "url": "https://fifaworld-cup-2026.org/fifa-world-cup-2026-tickets"
};
---

<Layout 
  title="FIFA World Cup 2026 Tickets: Prices, Dates & Official Sales" 
  description="Check the official cost of FIFA World Cup 2026 tickets, sales dates for the general public, and where to buy them safely."
  schema={ticketsSchema}
>
  <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-8 text-blue-900 tracking-tight">
    FIFA World Cup 2026 Tickets: Sales, Prices and Locations
  </h1>
  
  <article class="prose lg:prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
    <p>
      The 2026 World Cup will take place in Mexico, the United States, and Canada, which has generated great enthusiasm among fans who want to be present at the matches. Below, check the <strong>fifa world cup 2026 tickets</strong> cost, sales dates for the general public, and the place of purchase.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Official Sales Phases and Schedule</h2>
    <p>
      The 2026 World Cup will begin on June 11 at the Estadio Azteca in Mexico City, where the Tri and South Africa will face each other in the opening match, and will conclude on Sunday, July 19, with the grand final at MetLife Stadium. The <strong>fifa world cup 2026 tickets</strong> sale will be carried out in several stages, starting from September 10 and ending on July 19, 2026, the day of the tournament final.
    </p>
    <p>
      Each of these stages could vary in terms of purchase methods, payment options, and types of <strong>fifa world cup 2026 tickets</strong> available. Specific details about each phase will be released in the coming months. Fans who register and create a FIFA ID will receive updated information on the dates and the sales process.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">World Cup Draw and Entry Requirements</h2>
    <p>
      On the other hand, the World Cup draw will take place starting at 12:00 PM (local time) on Friday, December 5, at the Kennedy Center in Washington DC, where the groups will be established and the matches scheduled, including venues and times. Additionally, FIFA points out that acquiring <strong>fifa world cup 2026 tickets</strong> does not guarantee entry to the host countries, so it advises consulting the official government pages of Canada, Mexico, and the United States for entry requirements.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">World Cup 2026: Ticket Resale and Hospitality Packages</h2>
    
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">Official Resale Platform</h3>
    <p>
      Likewise, ticket owners who meet the necessary conditions now have an official resale platform managed by FIFA at FIFA.com/tickets. This initiative seeks to protect fans from invalid or unauthorized resales and is available to followers subject to federal and local regulations; residents in Mexico will have access to the FIFA ticket exchange market for their <strong>fifa world cup 2026 tickets</strong>.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">Hospitality and Enhanced Experience</h3>
    <p>
      Fans wishing to secure their attendance at specific matches and enjoy an enhanced experience on the day of the event can purchase packages that include <strong>fifa world cup 2026 tickets</strong>, which can be found at FIFA.com/hospitality, through On Location, the official hospitality provider for the FIFA World Cup 2026.
    </p>
  </article>

  <div class="mt-12 p-8 bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl border border-blue-100 text-center">
    <p class="text-blue-900 font-bold mb-4">Stay updated on all ticket sales phases</p>
    <a href="https://www.fifa.com/en/tickets" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-blue-900 text-white font-black px-8 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-800 transition-colors">
      Official FIFA Ticket Portal
    </a>
  </div>
</Layout>